# ai-sprint CLI

A command-line tool for standardizing sprint lifecycle management and `.sprint` directory organization patterns.

## Installation

```bash
pip install ai-sprint
```

## Usage

```bash
# Initialize a new sprint structure
ai-sprint init

# Start a task
ai-sprint start "Implement user login"

# Check sprint status
ai-sprint status

# Finish the current task
ai-sprint finish
```
